* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ˈkæm.ɹə/|/ˈkæm.ə(ɹ).ə}} {{SAMPA|/"k{m.r@/|/"k{m.@(r).@/}}
* {{audio|en-us-camera.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A device for taking still or moving pictures or [[photograph]]s.
